text: Supernatural Birth Machine is the fourth album of British doom metal band Cathedral, released in October 1996 by Earache. ==Track listing== ==Personnel== ===Cathedral=== * Lee Dorrian – vocals * Garry Jennings – guitar, mellotron (1, 5), piano (6) * Leo Smee – bass * Brian Dixon – drums ===Technical personnel=== * Kit Woolven – production, engineering * Doug Cook – assistant engineering * Noel Summerville – mastering * Antz White – art direction, design, digital image manipulation * Dave Patchett – cover painting * George Chin – band photographs ==References== Category:Cathedral (band) albums Category:1996 albums Category:Earache Records albums
